list.comment: In this edition, I completed edited and abstracted the ContactList class, I added new methods and mainly completed the run() function and all its helper functions. I also added comments to ContactList. I also fixed the formatting of things that were printed out into the console to make it easier to use and comprehend.

task.summary: In this edition of ContactList, I added 4 classes: Person, Student, Teacher, and ContactList.
